    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "FROM : A. H. Belmont",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "DATE: August 2[unclear]/1950",
      "status": "needs_image_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "SUBJECT: SUMMARY OF AERIAL",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "PHENOMENA IN NEW MEXICO",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "MISCELLANEOUS - INFORMATION CONCERNING",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "PURPOSE",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "To advise that: (1) OSI has expressed concern in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "connection with the continued appearance of unexplained phenomena",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "described as green fireballs, discs and meteors in the vicinity",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "of sensitive installations in New Mexico. (2) [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "[REDACTED] of the University of New Mexico, reported that the phenomena",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "does not appear to be of meteoric origin. (3) OSI has contracted",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "with [REDACTED], Alamogordo, New Mexico, to make scientific",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "study of the unexplained phenomena.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "NATURE OF PHENOMENA",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "Observations of aerial phenomena occurring within the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "vicinity of sensitive installations have been recorded by the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "Air Force since December, 1948. The phenomena have been",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "classified into 3 general types which are identified as follows:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "1. Green fireballs, objects moving at high speed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "in shapes resembling half moons, circles and discs emitting",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "green light.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "2. Discs, round flat shaped objects or phenomena",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "moving at fast velocity and emitting a brilliant white light",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "or reflected light.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "3. Meteors, aerial phenomena resembling meteoric",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "material moving at high velocity and varying in color.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "The above phenomena have been reported to vary in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "color from brilliant white to amber, red and green.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "Since 1948, approximately 150 observations of aerial",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "phenomena referred to above have been recorded in the vicinity",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "of installations in New Mexico. A number of observations have",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "been reported by different reliable individuals at approximately",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "the same time.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "status": "blank"
    },
